{"tid":2314353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台中出現喪屍虎頭蜂，兇殘咬甩警察一塊皮！","createTime":"2020-12-06T13:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T11:36:11.000Z","uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b38c8ef442a5ed904a7646ceae8604324bf8b983","tid":2314353,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"時序入秋後偶有虎頭蜂在野外攻擊登山客意外，但台中市德基水庫卻發生罕見的虎頭蜂吃人肉案例！保二總隊德基小隊小隊長張文勇5日上班時，巡視廳舍外面時遇到一隻虎頭蜂駐足他左耳不肯飛走，他擔心被螫咬，小心翼翼移步到廁所，讓牠逗留約5分鐘才趁機打死，但耳輪被咬走一塊表皮組織，有輕微水腫瘀青。執業25年的耳鼻喉科醫師黃山崧說，他在臨床上從未接獲虎頭蜂咬人肉案例，佩服張的冷靜、真是奇人軼事。苗縣府自然生態保育科長張葦表示，從未聽過虎頭蜂咬人不叮人案例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4x7Qnat.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4x7Qnat.png&h=0f033ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這隻虎頭蜂停在張文勇左耳約5分鐘，不斷啃咬耳廓表皮組織<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddEjfv0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddEjfv0.png&h=b32e9f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n耳廓的表皮組織被咬掉一小塊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WW6JHa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWW6JHa5.png&h=dab7b197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狠咬警察張文勇耳朵表皮肉，下場當然被碎屍萬段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201206/7FIGEGCO3NCVDLYFM4IBHUKL4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201206%2F7FIGEGCO3NCVDLYFM4IBHUKL4Q%2F&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2vkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=a326ba1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201206%2F7FIGEGCO3NCVDLYFM4IBHUKL4Q%2F&h=7a70d374\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201206/7FIGEGCO3NCVDLYFM4IBHUKL4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"f8c80c62a2656c63531abe12c34ff6e02a97738f","tid":2314353,"uid":374986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src